    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Monitor logs from physical access control systems (e.g., badge readers) to find unusual access patterns (e.g., deviations from the norm) and failed access attempts
Ex2: Review and monitor physical access records (e.g., from visitor registration, sign-in sheets)
Ex3: Monitor physical access controls (e.g., locks, latches, hinge pins, alarms) for signs of tampering
Ex4: Monitor the physical environment using alarm systems, cameras, and security guards"""@en ;
