    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Establish criteria for determining the criticality of capabilities and services as viewed by internal and external stakeholders
Ex2: Determine (e.g., from a business impact analysis) assets and business operations that are vital to achieving mission objectives and the potential impact of a loss (or partial loss) of such operations
Ex3: Establish and communicate resilience objectives (e.g., recovery time objectives) for delivering critical capabilities and services in various operating states (e.g., under attack, during recovery, normal operation)"""@en ;
