    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Review audit findings to confirm whether the existing cybersecurity strategy has ensured compliance with internal and external requirements
Ex2: Review the performance oversight of those in cybersecurity-related roles to determine whether policy changes are necessary
Ex3: Review strategy in light of cybersecurity incidents"""@en ;
