    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Review key performance indicators (KPIs) to ensure that organization-wide policies and procedures achieve objectives
Ex2: Review key risk indicators (KRIs) to identify risks the organization faces, including likelihood and potential impact
Ex3: Collect and communicate metrics on cybersecurity risk management with senior leadership"""@en ;
