        csfref:SP-800-53-Rev-5-2-0-SR-02 ;
    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Aggregate and manage cybersecurity risks alongside other enterprise risks (e.g., compliance, financial, operational, regulatory, reputational, safety)
Ex2: Include cybersecurity risk managers in enterprise risk management planning
Ex3: Establish criteria for escalating cybersecurity risks within enterprise risk management"""@en ;
