    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Determine how to update senior executives, directors, and management on the organization's cybersecurity posture at agreed-upon intervals
Ex2: Identify how all departments across the organization - such as management, operations, internal auditors, legal, acquisition, physical security, and HR - will communicate with each other about cybersecurity risks"""@en ;
