    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Integrate cybersecurity risk management considerations into human resources processes (e.g., personnel screening, onboarding, change notification, offboarding)
Ex2: Consider cybersecurity knowledge to be a positive factor in hiring, training, and retention decisions
Ex3: Conduct background checks prior to onboarding new personnel for sensitive roles, and periodically repeat background checks for personnel with such roles
Ex4: Define and enforce obligations for personnel to be aware of, adhere to, and uphold security policies as they relate to their roles"""@en ;
