    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Maintain a list of the designated data types of interest (e.g., personally identifiable information, protected health information, financial account numbers, organization intellectual property, operational technology data)
Ex2: Continuously discover and analyze ad hoc data to identify new instances of designated data types
Ex3: Assign data classifications to designated data types through tags or labels
