    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Use cyber threat intelligence to maintain awareness of the types of threat actors likely to target the organization and the TTPs they are likely to use
Ex2: Perform threat hunting to look for signs of threat actors within the environment
Ex3: Implement processes for identifying internal threat actors"""@en ;
