        csfref:SP-800-53-Rev-5-2-0-PE-20,
        csfref:SSDF-PO-5-2 ;
    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Use security guards, security cameras, locked entrances, alarm systems, and other physical controls to monitor facilities and restrict access
Ex2: Employ additional physical security controls for areas that contain high-risk assets
Ex3: Escort guests, vendors, and other third parties within areas that contain business-critical assets"""@en ;
