    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: When risk warrants it, restrict software execution to permitted products only or deny the execution of prohibited and unauthorized software
Ex2: Verify the source of new software and the software's integrity before installing it
Ex3: Configure platforms to use only approved DNS services that block access to known malicious domains
Ex4: Configure platforms to allow the installation of organization-approved software only"""@en ;
