        csfref:SP-800-53-Rev-5-2-0-IR-08 ;
    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Prepare an after-action report that documents the incident itself, the response and recovery actions taken, and lessons learned
Ex2: Declare the end of incident recovery once the criteria are met"""@en ;
    csfprop:informativeReferenceText """CRI Profile v2.0: RC.RP-06
