        csfref:SP-800-53-Rev-5-1-1-IR-04,
        csfref:SP-800-53-Rev-5-2-0-AU-07,
        csfref:SP-800-53-Rev-5-2-0-IR-04,
        csfref:SP-800-53-Rev-5-2-0-SI-02-07 ;
    csfprop:implementationExample """Ex1: Determine the sequence of events that occurred during the incident and which assets and resources were involved in each event
Ex2: Attempt to determine what vulnerabilities, threats, and threat actors were directly or indirectly involved in the incident
Ex3: Analyze the incident to find the underlying, systemic root causes
Ex4: Check any cyber deception technology for additional information on attacker behavior"""@en ;
